item.title: First Post!
item.description: Today I created blog using Jekyll, which I’ll be using to document some stuff that’s going on here in ATX. This may or may not include: Front End Web Dev research and projects, house remodel projects and thoughts, outdoor pursuits, and an ongoing list of meals that I’d like my wife to cook for me.
